OL,3,CThree charged in connection with
OL,4,CKenilworth murder investigation
OL,6,FThree people have been charged in
OL,7,Fconnection with a murder investigation
OL,8,Finto the death of a man inside a house
OL,9,Fin Kenilworth.
OL,11,FPolice and paramedics were called to
OL,12,Fthe house on Chesnut Avenue just
OL,13,Fbefore midnight on Friday after
OL,14,Fconcerns were raised for the welfare
OL,15,Fof a man.
OL,17,FThe man in his 40s died shortly
OL,18,Fafterwards.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
