OL,3,CThree charged in connection with
OL,4,CKenilworth murder investigation
OL,6,FOn Monday 23 March 24-year-old Lewis
OL,7,FDowling, of Yarnfield Road in
OL,8,FBirmingham, 49-year-old Patricia
OL,9,FDowling, of Chestnut Avenue in
OL,10,FKenilworth, and a 16-year-old boy from
OL,11,FKenilworth, who can't be named for
OL,12,Flegal reasons, were charged with
OL,13,Fmurder.
OL,15,FAll three, who are white British, were
OL,16,Fremanded in custody to appear at
OL,17,FCoventry Magistrates' Court on Tuesday
OL,18,F24 March.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
