OL,3,CThree charged in connection with
OL,4,CKenilworth murder investigation
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Charlie
OL,7,FNaughton said: "Specially trained
OL,8,Fofficers are supporting the victim's
OL,9,Ffamily.
OL,11,F"At this time, we believe the incident
OL,12,Fwas contained to the house and there
OL,13,Fis no risk to the wider public.
OL,15,F"I know this will cause a great deal
OL,16,Fof shock in the local community. We'll
OL,17,Fhave officers in the area and I'd
OL,18,Fencourage anyone with information to
OL,19,Fspeak to one of them."
